    public class OWLProfileViolation
extends Object
    Describes a violation of an OWLProfile by an axiom. Ultimately, there may be part of the axiom that violates the profile rather than the complete axiom.
    Author:
    Matthew Horridge, The University of Manchester, Information Management Group, Date: 03-Aug-2009
